WEBVTT

00:00.043 --> 00:02.359
Previously on "Once Upon a Time"...

00:02.362 --> 00:03.918
- Who are you?
- I'm your daughter.

00:03.921 --> 00:05.044
I don't have a daughter.

00:05.047 --> 00:07.328
You just don't remember
because you're cursed.

00:07.331 --> 00:10.239
Come with me to my
neighborhood, Hyperion Heights.

00:10.242 --> 00:12.408
You can meet your true
love... Cinderella.

00:12.410 --> 00:15.145
My step-grandma, Cinderella's
step-mom, is trying

00:15.147 --> 00:17.080
to bring people from this world in

00:17.082 --> 00:19.182
so all the fairy-tale
characters move out.

00:19.184 --> 00:21.885
Everyone will lose
each other... forever.

